00124 // Morph controller method
00125 // NORMALIZED implies that the morph targets all have absolute vertex positions
00126 // RELATIVE implies that the morph targets have relative vertex positions
00127 //
00128 // Whether the vertex position is relative or absolute is irrelevant,
00129 // as long as you use the correct weight generation function:
00130 // NORMALIZED: base_weight = 1.0f - SUM(weight[t])
00131 // RELATIVE: base_weight = 1.0f
00132 // and position[k] = SUM(weight[t][k] * position[t][k])
00133 namespace FUDaeMorphMethod
00134 {
00135     enum Method
00136     {
00137         NORMALIZED = 0,
00138         RELATIVE,
00139 
00140         UNKNOWN,
00141         DEFAULT = NORMALIZED,
00142     };
00143 
00144     FCOLLADA_EXPORT Method FromString(const char* value);
00145     FCOLLADA_EXPORT const char* ToString(Method method);
00146     inline Method FromString(const fm::string& value) { return FromString(value.c_str()); }
00147 };
